Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ignore the lack of Olympic success by the Super Falcons.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody in this \\\"group of death\\\" is going to be content seeing them in this group, especially after the performance the world witnessed last summer.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This African outfit has flare in bunches up top with the likes of Asisat Oshoala and Uchenna Kanu, but its mentality defensively is what took this nation to the next level in 2023.\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asisat_Oshoala\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Asisat Oshoala\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asisat_Oshoala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asisat_Oshoala\"}, {\"begin\": 631, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uchenna_Kanu\", \"score\": 0.9999999956198735, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Uchenna Kanu\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uchenna_Kanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uchenna_Kanu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Randy Waldrum's team did not lose a match in normal time at the 2023 WWC, holding three opponents scoreless in regulation including Canada, the reigning gold medalists, and England, the 2022 European champions.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Randy Waldrum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\"}, {\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Wrestling_Council\", \"score\": 0.999999970294994, \"rank\": 2.9704875628470902e-08, \"text\": \"WWC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Wrestling_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Wrestling_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.928808248637397e-17, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999988277536473, \"rank\": 1.172248106399398e-05, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9512380517580059, \"rank\": 0.05126156186849069, \"text\": \"2022 European\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_European_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nigeria just looks like a more cohesive unit, using those solid defensive foundations to kick start attacks in the other direction.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We sent a message based on our performance at the World Cup.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never been one to use the media as my outlet to brag about our team,\\\"said Waldrum.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I do not think any of the three teams in our group will be underestimating us after what they saw at the World Cup.\\\"\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil, on the other hand, would rather forget what occurred on the big stage around this time last year.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.402373568059184e-21, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After cruising to a 4-0 win over Panama in the first game of the group play, the eight-time Copa Am\\u00c3\\u00a9rica Femenina winners collapsed, dropping points to France and Jamaica as it exited before the tournament really even started.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5692841788297494, \"rank\": 0.756591939820998, \"text\": \"Panama\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999861970538, \"rank\": 1.3802732728642726e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999991337063, \"rank\": 8.661403951343291e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gone are the days of Pia Sundhage.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pia_Sundhage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pia Sundhage\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pia_Sundhage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pia_Sundhage\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This team is now led by the ex-\\tCorinthians sideline leader Arthur Elias, who made some quite interesting roster decisions for this Olympics.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Club_Corinthians_Paulista\", \"score\": 0.9999999185342892, \"rank\": 8.146593691872424e-08, \"text\": \"Corinthians\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Club_Corinthians_Paulista\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Club_Corinthians_Paulista\"}, {\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Arthur\", \"score\": 0.99989781009196, \"rank\": 0.00010220035196397202, \"text\": \"Arthur\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Arthur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Arthur\"}, {\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\", \"score\": 0.999983395150667, \"rank\": 1.6605125256780667e-05, \"text\": \"Elias\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than summoning the fit Debinha, a standout player of Kansas City Current, Elias took a gamble by bringing in Kerolin, another exceptional talent who has not participated in any competitive football matches since October 2023.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1917, \"end\": 1936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_Current\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kansas City Current\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_Current\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_Current\"}, {\"begin\": 1938, \"end\": 1943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\", \"score\": 0.999983395150667, \"rank\": 1.6605125256780667e-05, \"text\": \"Elias\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\"}, {\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerolin_Nicoli_Israel_Ferraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kerolin\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerolin_Nicoli_Israel_Ferraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerolin_Nicoli_Israel_Ferraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the cost of an even longer absence, it does not make much sense as to why Brazil is seemingly rushing the 2023 NWSL MVP back.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2167, \"end\": 2173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.402373568059184e-21, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NWSL_awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NWSL MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NWSL_awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NWSL_awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, As Canarinhas' attack flourished in the lead up to the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elias' team beat Jamaica, the side that held it scoreless at the last World Cup, 8-0 on aggregate across two June friendlies.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999991337063, \"rank\": 8.661403951343291e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not the first time Nigeria will take on Marta and Brazil in the group stages of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2456, \"end\": 2463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.198921875011951e-43, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso